{"tid":9500,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[聖誕派暖] 整左幾份禮物但送唔出  想係度派左佢","createTime":"2016-11-28T15:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T22:14:08.000Z","uid":35702,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c82562c5b1c181acaf3225906ef339ecda21a2","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"利申先, 我係巴<br />\n入到黎幻想有絲打整禮物俾你既可以負評上一頁<br />\n<br />\n本身整左幾份小禮物諗住送俾佢<br />\n但依加冇機會<br />\n留係度督眼督鼻不如送晒俾各位巴絲等大家開心一秒都好<br />\n<br />\n首先有個用聖誕starfuck杯整嘅燈<br />\n開著左之後都好花下<br />\n建議咁多位當長夜燈用<br />\n<br />\n之後有個天氣瓶<br />\n呢個唔洗多講相信大家都知咩樣<br />\n個樽係燈泡型<br />\n大概好似一罐可樂咁上下大<br />\n<br />\n之後係座枱月歷<br />\n買齊晒料整<br />\n諗住開ig shop賣<br />\n不過俾眾多朋友極力反對<br />\n個概念係一塊有磁力既水松墊<br />\n有個木框鑲起佢<br />\n上面每個日子都係磁石貼黎<br />\n可以自己移位<br />\n又可以係日期果一格zip mimo紙或者statement提自己找數<br />\n<br />\n買左唔整又好晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但整好有冇人送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人會想收留佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86fa2adc2a7a6e2c29851f4c2df59006ca14c5b","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"利申呢排冇返屋企<br />\n圖後補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79661a30f91eedeb13df5379903e03f759df32eb","tid":9500,"uid":28700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:26:55.000Z","msg":"Ching咁好心機不如長期開Ig shop啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed6e9f1f665dff89c5d53f805db7d8f29ff9aa4","tid":9500,"uid":16477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"巴打咩事呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女已經有仔？"},{"pid":"f693a9a7a95fcfda243d2a7dfc5497780306fb7f","tid":9500,"uid":19267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"想要個天氣瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過巴打點解啲朋友叫唔好就唔開ig shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪有咩其他理由"},{"pid":"1ce5ff70c154607f83dc29ae62aa759d5c6a4e0d","tid":9500,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"襯就聖誕節，希望巴打好快走出傷痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd71791ee8e52b3fb8edd59435444bcd2f2d50a","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ching咁好心機不如長期開Ig shop啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學業繁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceacfead80fa810d10d97147b2caf078906e702","tid":9500,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"樓主做聖誕老人啦<br />\n記得唔好拋唔中份禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小心駕駛鹿車"},{"pid":"78288ae91423d5639c09e9c00a02080d9518c567","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:42:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想要個天氣瓶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過巴打點解啲朋友叫唔好就唔開ig shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪有咩其他理由</blockquote><br />\n佢地分析得幾好<br />\n1.唔係乜野好技術，剪剪貼貼係人都做到<br />\n冇本錢賣得貴<br />\n<br />\n2.海關捉得嚴, 用卡通人物做賣點遲早俾人拉，唔用卡通人物純粹用顏色, 擺位去吸引人相信好少人會買<br />\n<br />\n3.承接住1.同2. 唔賣得貴，整一個可能要個幾鐘，價位都係100樓下，計埋成本可能淨賺4.50蚊，呢家炒散都唔止呢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.即使食到頭啖水，都會有好多人湧入黎做，監生拉低個價"},{"pid":"8df2faff09c1c901d21acb753416949ffdeb6c06","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打咩事呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女已經有仔？</blockquote><br />\n好多野複雜<br />\n佢有上LIHKG<br />\n唔方便講<br />\n只係覺得佢離我越黎越遠"},{"pid":"de4cf7ff93d4beae3a4e4f6f729c7ed3805dda2e","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做聖誕老人啦<br />\n記得唔好拋唔中份禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小心駕駛鹿車</blockquote><br />\n你試下帶綠色聖誕帽<br />\n咁會易睇d"},{"pid":"4c578b6a5d9abeda2357ca4c1b98f606440eca18","tid":9500,"uid":727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"我想收禮物 毒撚一個未收過"},{"pid":"2b5bdd2a920998a51f2f25dcc779e04c031aae03","tid":9500,"uid":727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:45:17.000Z","msg":"[quote]我想收禮物 毒撚一個未收過[/<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> quote]"},{"pid":"84bb5d1b23bd2d129859b319c1c4eb9b7af995ed","tid":9500,"uid":1276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:47:30.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你送咩比我都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7bf532c97b7d519e9c4b896b3e87c66c2c54bd","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想收禮物 毒撚一個未收過</blockquote><br />\n記住臨近聖誕推返上來<br />\n我驚我會唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb03c48037e3b0eb589b631a0527b954163ec2b1","tid":9500,"uid":8213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"巴打振作呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你有個開心既聖誕節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw我樂意接受你d禮物<br />\n杯/天氣瓶都ok<br />\n等我呢隻單身狗有返d溫暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e610b9c5f81b0f1ab8efdc92bb11633805036d61","tid":9500,"uid":35702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"